title: TUESDAY 2/2 - Opening night of Super Bowl week
itunes:title: TUESDAY 2/2 - Opening night of Super Bowl week
description:
The Chiefs with a little concerning news (0:08) as two players are placed on the Reserve/COVID-19 list. Opening night did not disappoint...we'll hear from Patrick Mahomes (0:53) and Tom Brady discusses retirement plans (1:39). Plus Gronk being Gronk as he let's the cat out the bag on his offseason workout program (2:17). And, Packers coach Matt LaFleur fills us in on Aaron Rodgers' future in Green Bay (3:24)
